, la mayor inversi\u00f3n en restauraci\u00f3n ha sido realizada por SADER, seguida de CONAFOR con valores de 62% y 34%. Seguidamente, se ubica CONAZA y CONANP con 3% y 0.3% respectivamente (figura 14).", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e1bc37d1-c4bd-43e5-b952-4e727955fc42": {"__data__": {"id_": "e1bc37d1-c4bd-43e5-b952-4e727955fc42", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/aplicacion-del-barometro-de-la-restauracion-en-mexico", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Aplicaci\u00f3n del Bar\u00f3metro de la Restauraci\u00f3n en M\u00e9xico", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/aplicacion-del-barometro-de-la-restauracion-en-mexico", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "11165432e4c1368e24485e58e5530024058f99fb50108c1b1db4698d652fdfe4"}, "2": {"node_id": "6433ddbb-efab-45e4-b167-56e9626c1103", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/aplicacion-del-barometro-de-la-restauracion-en-mexico", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "19c551b164d83b667255b8c1aaafa641bb90ea23d100285321dc153982c96a4c"}}, "hash": "1a17955eb7c9886a7ddad160f9231a5760e78f8bb7955376b2df1ff2a0191674", "text": "Gasto p\u00fablico relativo a protecci\u00f3n del ambiente destinado a acciones de restauraci\u00f3n en M\u00e9xico durante el periodo 2011-2020 De acuer